I have been going to this place since I was a kid and I still love it till this day. Best slices in Sunset hands down. I have tried all their slices and pies and you can really tell that they use good ingredients not that cheap crap.  The employees are so funny they always make us laugh and they are always smiling and aim to please. I am a picky person and i'm sure if this was any other place I would have gotten attitudes for the special orders i place, I know i can be a pain but they certainly never make me feel that way. They always willing to make their customers happy and comfortable. Great place for dinner too. I love their menus( the lasagna is my families personal favorite) . The menu is big for whatever me and my family is in the mood for. They even deliver Ice Cream, Shakes and any Icy you want. Who does that around here? They are just awesome love you Dominick's ! Please dont ever change !   And if anyone gives you any less than 4 stars they probably did not order right or they just don't know what they are talking about, theres no way anyone can say this place has bad anything.
